ëíŸ@a481311846b53043fafdfb99320eb6ab6eebff56d742eb69046110d4aed146e6⁄	Title: This week in Nu #56
Path: This week in Nu #56
Content:
LhKipp posted a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/rfcs/blob/f0f9e384e0307d4039631fb1ef5fbb420301a9c3/text/0004-type-deduction.md] new RFC
 about extending our type inference logic and how we might extend the logic for working with aliases.
notryanb updated the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/cookbook/pull/17] git parsing examples in the cookbook
gorogoroumaru extended 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2529] ``math avg``
 to work with durations
andrasio extended the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2538] folding logic to work with tables
, improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2544] plugin loading and testing
, cleaned up 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2559] configuration reading
gillespiecd switched 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2540] active shell to be displayed as a boolean
, did some 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2543] code cleanup around booleans
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2560] removed 
``trim``
 in favor of 
``str trim``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2566] cleaned up the help text
radekvit added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2541] non-inclusive ranges
, made 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2550] ctrl-c work during sleep
, cleaned up 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2563] logic for 
``get``
 and 
``nu-value-ext``
jonathandturner fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2542] yanked crossterm version
fdncred and jonathandturner updated the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2565] rustyline version
, fixing some instability during line editing
lidin fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2547] rawkey for ARM
fdncred fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2548] ctrl-c issue
, added a few more 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2553] ansi escape sequences
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2569] replace all to 
``str find-replace``
thegedge refactored 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2555] the completion trait
rezural added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2556] case-sensitive/case-insensitive completion matching
